and watch him suffer

17:53.330 --> 17:54.582
when I know
that I could help.

17:54.630 --> 17:56.325
But, still,
the thought of Stella

17:56.370 --> 17:58.111
helping Dr. Grant feels --

17:58.160 --> 18:03.849
And the thought of Pippa helping
Wes, it just feels similarly...

18:03.900 --> 18:05.117
Super not good.

18:05.170 --> 18:07.116
Extra super.

