dollars to afford college.

18:56.830 --> 18:58.514
-I want to,

18:58.570 --> 19:01.301
_ but it's —-
it's too expensive.

19:01.350 --> 19:02.693
And the last time
I checked,

19:02.750 --> 19:04.263
they not giving out
scholarships to people

19:04.310 --> 19:06.176
who are older than dust.

19:06.230 --> 19:07.391
You're not old.

19:07.450 --> 19:08.963
Honestly,
there are sometimes

19:09.010 --> 19:10.739
that I think it's mathematically
impossible for you

19:10.800 --> 19:11.870
to be Lizzie's mother.

19:11.930 --> 19:13.625
You know,
I do look young.

19:13.670 --> 19:16.970
