with your mom.

20:09.940 --> 20:13.240
When Stella was sick,
I did what I thought was right,

20:13.290 --> 20:17.818
but I didn't ask your mom what
she thought, which was wrong.

20:19.470 --> 20:22.349
That's not how
partnership works.

20:22.390 --> 20:25.473
But what if I'm right?

20:27.000 --> 20:29.264
Then you'll
convince him.

20:29.310 --> 20:31.483
Or you compromise.

20:31.530 --> 20:33.089
Or you end up alone.

20:33.140 --> 20:35.450
Yeah.

20:35.490 --> 20:38.664
Hey, I'm really
proud of you.

20:38.710 --> 20:40.269
And I don't want you
to screw this up

20:40.320 --> 20:43.711
because you're acting like me,
so talk to Wes.

20:43.760 --> 20:46.195
I will.
And for the record,

20:46.240 --> 20:49.289
acting like you wouldn't be
the worst thing in the world.

20:49.330 --> 20:51.025
Although, I'm gonna need you
to back off my sundae,

20:51.070 --> 20:52.287
