like a pig.

20:52.330 --> 20:54.116
Aw, come on.

20:54.160 --> 20:55.764
No, go ahead.

20:58.600 --> 21:02.514
Okay, I just have
a few more errands to run.

21:02.560 --> 21:04.346
And then I will
meet you at the bar.

21:04.390 --> 21:07.439
Have you heard more from
Pippa about the investor?

21:07.480 --> 21:08.777
Not yet.

21:08.830 --> 21:11.049
And, Stella, I promise,
if she hadn't offered --

21:11.090 --> 21:14.435
It's fine. We're fine.
You heard what Miles said.

21:14.490 --> 21:17.528
We are fully committed and we
have nothing to be afraid of.

21:17.580 --> 21:19.924
