another call, though.

21:19.970 --> 21:21.745
Go.
I'll see you soon.

21:21.800 --> 21:23.484
Okay.

21:23.540 --> 21:25.190
Hello?
Dr. Grant: Hey.

21:25.240 --> 21:30.360
Uh, well, I'm sending up
the Bat-Signal.

21:30.410 --> 21:34.449
Uh, you got a second
to talk?

21:34.510 --> 21:35.807
What's up?

21:35.850 --> 21:40.947
Well, uh, my blood alcohol
level, for starters.

21:40.990 --> 21:42.242
Wait, I thought you were
supposed to be

21:42.300 --> 21:45.383
