trying to make it all better

22:31.260 --> 22:33.774
and just...

22:33.830 --> 22:36.049
just be there.

22:36.090 --> 22:38.252
For them.

22:38.310 --> 22:39.562
For him.

22:40.750 --> 22:44.527
Sounds like he has
some pretty good advice.

22:44.580 --> 22:47.618
Yeah.
Yeah, he did.

22:49.890 --> 22:51.665
Hey, Stella, thank you.

22:53.540 --> 22:56.805
And, um,
good luck tonight.

22:58.550 --> 23:00.496
Yeah. You, too.

23:00.550 --> 23:02.245
Bye.

23:05.940 --> 23:08.420
