24:24.890 --> 24:26.710
You know,
this is kind of thing

24:26.760 --> 24:28.671
that we should
probably consult about.

24:28.720 --> 24:29.892
Right, partner?

24:29.940 --> 24:32.250
Um, would you excuse us
for just one second?

24:35.730 --> 24:37.425
So...what do we think?

24:37.470 --> 24:38.858
Because generally speaking,
I make it a point

24:38.910 --> 24:40.730
