makes me feel calm.

25:15.810 --> 25:17.460
Still.

25:17.510 --> 25:18.727
Considering
the circumstances,

25:18.770 --> 25:20.374
probably best to find
someone else.

25:20.430 --> 25:22.467
Totally, and now we don't even
have to tell Stella

25:22.520 --> 25:23.646
