right?

25:23.690 --> 25:25.772
Right.
Total non-issue.

25:28.740 --> 25:32.563
Hi. Look who I found here.
It's your new business partner.

25:32.610 --> 25:34.339
Actually, she's not.

25:34.400 --> 25:36.653
